methods.plotStyle:
Returns the requested plot style.

:param style: (java.lang.String) - case insensitive style name
:return: (io.deephaven.plot.PlotStyle) PlotStyle with the given name
methods.plotStyleNames:
Returns the names of available plot styles.

:return: (java.lang.String[]) array of the PlotStyle names
methods.valueOf:
Returns the enum constant of this type with the specified name.
The string must match exactly an identifier used to declare an
enum constant in this type.  (Extraneous whitespace characters are 
not permitted.)

:param name: (java.lang.String) - the name of the enum constant to be returned.
:return: (io.deephaven.plot.PlotStyle) the enum constant with the specified name
methods.values:
Returns an array containing the constants of this enum type, in
the order they are declared.

:return: (io.deephaven.plot.PlotStyle[]) an array containing the constants of this enum type, in the order they are declared

text: The style of a plot (e.g. line, bar, etc.).
